Articles.Content:
Hi

Whenever I start a flight I see the message

"RasterPropMonitor Initialization Error Check Config"

I have tried reinstalling the mod, have one version of the latest module manager and are running many other mods including the b9 aerospace mod and the enhanced stock interiors mod. RPM worked for me once before but obviously does no longer.

Please take a look and my KSP.log file and advise how I can resolve this error. Thanks in advance.

p.s. sorry if I put this question in the wrong place or something I have never used this website before.
